data.description: Welcome home! This house has spectacular views of nature in the backyard from the covered deck. The family room also features a beautiful functional fireplace. This home has a tremendous amount of space for entertaining. Get the best of both worlds with a rural feel, and prime location in a suburban area. It feels like you are miles away from Metro Atlanta while in reality the home is positioned close to major highways and interstates. The Master Bedroom has French Doors that lead out onto the covered deck and features a walk in closet, a beautiful walk in shower, and a jetted garden tub. The home also features a gigantic upstairs loft with a private bathroom. The family room features spectacular views of the tree line in the backyard which is incredible particularly when the season changes to Autumn. The neighborhood is quiet, clean, and the other homeowners' properties are well maintained.
